m_q.target_metric: The most recent year in which a pylon was built in Germany
sub_questions: Which rows have 'Germany' in the Country column?
What are the valid years in the 'Year built' column for German pylons?
What is the maximum/latest year among German pylon construction years?

scale_issues: Year built column has dtype 'object' instead of numeric, may contain non-numeric values

format_notes: Year built column contains mixed formats (single years like '1966', year ranges like '194?', text like 'Early 2012', and empty values)
Some Year built values are missing (empty strings)
Some Year built values contain uncertainty markers (e.g., '194?')
Some Year built values contain descriptive text (e.g., 'Early 2012')

constraints: Year built must be parseable as a valid year
Year built should not be empty or null for valid records
derived_filters: Filter out rows where Year built is empty or cannot be converted to a year
Extract numeric year from 'Year built' column handling various formats
output_format_requirements: Return a single year value (integer or string format)
Result should be the maximum year among all German pylon construction years
